About Us
At Chargcom, we are dedicated to powering the future of transportation by providing
reliable, efficient, and sustainable EV charger installation solutions. Based in
Chennai, Tamil Nadu. We specialize in installing a wide range of electric vehicle
charging stations for homes, businesses, and public spaces. Our mission is to
accelerate the adoption of electric vehicles by making charging infrastructure easily
accessible and hassle-free for everyone.
Our Mission
To empower the shift to electric mobility by providing
comprehensive EV charging solutions that are accessible,
affordable, and environmentally responsible.
Our Vision
A future where electric vehicle charging is as seamless and
ubiquitous as fueling a traditional vehicle, driving the world towards
a cleaner, greener tomorrow.
Residential EV Charger Installation: Whether you're a homeowner looking to install a charger or upgrade your current setup,
we offer customized solutions that fit your needs and budget.
Commercial EV Charger Installation: We partner with businesses, property managers, and developers to design and
implement scalable EV charging solutions, creating a future-proof environment for EV users.
Public Charging Stations: We assist local governments and private entities in installing public charging stations, supporting
the growing demand for accessible EV infrastructure.
Why Choose Us
Expertise & Experience: Our team of certified electricians and
technicians has extensive experience in EV charger installation and
is trained in the latest industry standards and best practices.
Sustainability Focus: We are committed to supporting the transition
to cleaner energy. By installing EV chargers, we contribute to
reducing carbon emissions and promoting a more sustainable future.
Customer-Centric Approach: From the initial consultation to post-
installation support, we prioritize our customers' needs, offering
transparent pricing, efficient installations, and responsive customer
service.
Cutting-Edge Technology: We work with top-tier brands and the
latest technologies to ensure that our customers receive high-quality,
reliable, and future-proof EV charging solutions.
